OL,3,CToo costly to spend a penny? Councils
OL,4,Cclosing public loos as part of budget
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FPublic toilets are becoming few and
OL,8,Ffar between, as council budget cuts
OL,9,Ftake effect. ITV News Presenter Faye
OL,10,FBarker has the latest
OL,12,Facross England are increasingly
OL,13,Fchoosing to close public toilets as
OL,14,Fpart of budget cuts.
OL,16,FResearch by ITV News has revealed that
OL,17,Fresidents in some towns will now
OL,18,Fstruggle to find any such facilities
OL,19,Fin use.
