OL,3,CToo costly to spend a penny? Councils
OL,4,Cclosing public loos as part of budget
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FHelen Ince told ITV News that a lack
OL,8,Fof public toilets could create issues
OL,9,Ffor people with specific medical needs
OL,10,F- such as pregnant women or those
OL,11,Fliving with diabetes.
OL,13,FShe said: "Feeling that awkwardness,
OL,14,Fone of the big things also is thinking
OL,15,Fthese kind of venues aren't always
OL,16,Fopen.
OL,18,F"You know they're open during the
OL,19,Fworking day, for example, might close
OL,20,Fabout 5pm, and then it might be pubs
OL,21,For other things that are open."
