OL,3,CToo costly to spend a penny? Councils
OL,4,Cclosing public loos as part of budget
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FIn the last decade, the British Toilet
OL,8,FAssociation (BTA) estimates that half
OL,9,Fof standalone toilets have closed.
OL,11,FThree quarters of people surveyed by
OL,12,Fthe BTA now feel there are not enough
OL,13,Fpublic toilets in their area, while
OL,14,Fone in five said they are leaving home
OL,15,Fless often as a result.
